WEBVTT

00:00.080 --> 00:02.370
Mom and Dad divorced.

00:03.110 --> 00:06.970
Dad hugged me on the day he left.

00:07.740 --> 00:10.060
I was happy to have him hug me.

00:10.060 --> 00:11.280
He was warm and gentle.

00:11.920 --> 00:13.910
I won’t see him for a while.

00:14.680 --> 00:17.830
I’m okay with being Dad’s daughter.

00:18.370 --> 00:19.990
I’m the one at fault.

00:20.450 --> 00:21.990
I’m the cause.

00:22.870 --> 00:25.880
I hurt Mom and Dad.

00:26.560 --> 00:28.170
I’m a bad kid.

00:29.060 --> 00:31.100
I don’t want Dad to leave.

00:31.790 --> 00:33.920
Will he hug me again?

00:34.470 --> 00:35.980
I’m sure I’ll see him again.
